WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.390 align:middle line:10%
>> The mysterious world
of dreams has, thus far,

00:00:03.390 --> 00:00:05.880 align:middle line:10%
only been fully
accessible to one person--

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:07.020 align:middle line:10%
the dreamer.

00:00:07.020 --> 00:00:10.470 align:middle line:84%
Until now, with a recent
groundbreaking study,

00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:13.770 align:middle line:84%
a new age of dream
research has just begun.

00:00:13.770 --> 00:00:15.745 align:middle line:90%
This is Gaia News.

